{"tid":1691800,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"覺唔覺得香港依家需要一個#strikechallege活動嚟喚醒對罷工嘅覺醒？","createTime":"2019-11-03T20:04:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T20:17:22.000Z","uid":180201,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"64fcec9e2e77626127253feb5331d0e344f2ffc6","tid":1691800,"uid":180201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T20:04:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">罷工：唔洗留血唔洗比人拉，對政府施好大壓力，但難實行</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n其實長期大罷工係最強武器<br />\n我唔返工起屋企 你班green object會唔會衝上樓叫人返工？收錢做嘢嘅籃絲會唔會上門斬你叫你返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 安全大，對政府壓力又大。但問題係發起長期大罷工係好難嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人要取得共識，再計劃行動</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n首先，我地香港人要有個共識先&mdash;是否同意採用大罷工呢招？我都見有post準備緊大罷工，同意嘅可以支持下同路人。<br />\n<br />\n不過我都想起到再作多次個統計先：<br />\n正皮：同意係時候發起長期大罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n負皮：罷工未係時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果大家都覺得係時候大罷工，咁應該點發起？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔罷工嘅心理壓力？（大家可以留言一齊分析）</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n其實唔罷工，一嚟係為咗生計，二嚟係因為見你左右都照返緊工，得自己一個罷工會好蝕底咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢種心理好現實，我絕對明白<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n如果大家見到身邊嘅朋友都罷工罷課，你會唔會有返安全感，想跟埋佢地一齊罷？</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n不如試下搞個#hkstrikechallenge？運用社交媒體同羊群心理嘅力量</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n就好似當年Ice Bucket Challenge咁<br />\n當年個個起ig見到有人自己拍片淋冰水落個自己頭到<br />\n再tag 3個朋友一係跟住做 一係就捐錢<br />\n然後個個都覺得幾有趣又跟住做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實有啲係純粹跟風<br />\n唔知背後目的係想引起大家對ALS嘅關注<br />\n<br />\n於是我起到諗<br />\n如果大家都搞類似嘅嘢叫人一齊罷工罷課<br />\n再起ig tag 3個人/更多你嘅朋友<br />\n大家又會跟住做的話再形成一股風氣跟風做<br />\n當中個ig story要落 #hkstrikechallenge<br />\n引起大家對擺工嘅關注 甚至真係叫到你嘅圈子嘅朋友罷工<br />\n然後你嘅朋友再叫佢圈子嘅人罷工<br />\n其實只要大家公開起自己社交媒體話同幾個朋友一齊罷<br />\n慢慢傳個風氣出去就會開始有人跟風<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以我地需要一個類似Ice bucket challenge 嘅嘢，大家跟風一齊長期罷工。但我細節未諗好，既然場運動都無大台，大家自由發揮，討論下？<br />\n<br />\n覺得有得諗嘅<br />\n可以留言傾下<br />\n歡迎留言文宣推post<br />\n<br />\n呢場運動，我地唔可以輸<br />\n你睇下新疆？"},{"pid":"9e7ecd261c0e54345d8220f4b42f0260e614dc97","tid":1691800,"uid":180201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T20:08:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LeWcLSn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLeWcLSn.jpg&h=a6c3d0e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19fa723746609e769232350097a69ad15b78afa1","tid":1691800,"uid":186800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T20:08:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>嘩 如果每人搵條鎖鏈鎖住大廈個閘，啲人出唔到街咪好大件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />千奇唔好咁做</blockquote><blockquote>如果全家都自罷就去令全幢返唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>如果大家都肯由自己屋企人搞起 你話條街仲有幾多人呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實罷工真係好易  首先令自己全家返唔到工先<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691699\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691699</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n方法就比左你 唔係搞到自己屋企人就唔制下話？"},{"pid":"e4da1ff04cad97a642803aa57c1ef9e3d65ecea2","tid":1691800,"uid":180201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19fa723746609e769232350097a69ad15b78afa1","tid":1691800,"uid":186800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T20:08:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>嘩 如果每人搵條鎖鏈鎖住大廈個閘，啲人出唔到街咪好大件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />千奇唔好咁做</blockquote><blockquote>如果全家都自罷就去令全幢返唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>如果大家都肯由自己屋企人搞起 你話條街仲有幾多人呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實罷工真係好易  首先令自己全家返唔到工先<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691699\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691699</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n方法就比左你 唔係搞到自己屋企人就唔制下話？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T20:09:33.000Z","msg":"跟機！"},{"pid":"147511fd2b9b148f0239215fce93d20fb0bddacc","tid":1691800,"uid":180201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T20:10:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/eyepressnews/videos/2204684136490751/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Feyepressnews%2Fvideos%2F2204684136490751%2F&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axGrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=06c4cb32\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/eyepressnews/videos/2204684136490751/</a>"},{"pid":"76cc51b171659da7deb59e4b56c03e83a66a5a4e","tid":1691800,"uid":180201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T20:12:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t14hW0w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft14hW0w.jpg&h=52c60340&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06a6279dc043723338a3da612a42653b9d935167","tid":1691800,"uid":180201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T20:13:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kVXCW0O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkVXCW0O.jpg&h=cfad360e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16d306595f051404bdce210a633aa4b8ea04e732","tid":1691800,"uid":180201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T20:13:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AOXSLUh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAOXSLUh.jpg&h=7793290f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46b10146ebf8a0629fdfe5aa8b0e78fd48881921","tid":1691800,"uid":180201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T20:14:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cQd6Qk5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcQd6Qk5.jpg&h=df5889e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9fbcfcb8886e66f41baedbdf22dcb587b2005d69","tid":1691800,"uid":186800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T20:14:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係潑冷水但how<br />\n反鎖大門？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多手足屋企人係藍絲<br />\n你強迫佢地罷工<br />\n根據藍絲阻人返工=最大罪 <br />\n同埋屋企人無錢/政府親既特性<br />\n分分鐘獅鳥埋手足</blockquote>而家偷偷地去熄佢鬧鐘 霸廁所 收銀包 收鞋 擋大門 自己揀樣啦</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><blockquote>嘩 如果每人搵條鎖鏈鎖住大廈個閘，啲人出唔到街咪好大件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />千奇唔好咁做</blockquote><blockquote>如果全家都自罷就去令全幢返唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>如果大家都肯由自己屋企人搞起 你話條街仲有幾多人呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實罷工真係好易  首先令自己全家返唔到工先<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691699\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691699</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n方法就比左你 唔係搞到自己屋企人就唔制下話？"},{"pid":"653e9ebb66af97247ca079e49af360044c888646","tid":1691800,"uid":180201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T20:15:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UBEUZeG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUBEUZeG.jpg&h=11749dd0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c487e4d906cdf1878037e8884d1ebd30dccf1ec","tid":1691800,"uid":180201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T20:15:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bJ73SzX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbJ73SzX.jpg&h=df8b6634&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28a26bc7a7ba6067069cb70eef388f836f87eb5e","tid":1691800,"uid":180201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T20:16:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ax05mtt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%